summary:
Rural living and mindset as basis for transformative ways of living and doing. Diverse economies as everyday activities. Notches of knowledge and understanding. 
I have a research master degree in international development studies specialized in rural sociology. I combine thinking and doing in daily practices, research and art to serve a good life for all living beings. I like to combine field practices with analytical work.
